{"tid":1766082,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"殺害示威者 伊拉克警判絞刑","createTime":"2019-12-02T10:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T12:37:59.000Z","uid":271123,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"91898fa888de20e7c27a08f92bef651b0dcc0356","tid":1766082,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:21:53.000Z","msg":"(星島日報報道)伊拉克一名警察少校周日被法庭裁定殺害示威者罪名成立，被判處絞刑，成為過去兩個月反政府示威以來，首名被判死刑的警察。<br />\n<br />\n　　伊拉克司法消息人士稱，南部庫特市刑事法庭就該市十一月二日有七名示威者被殺事件，判處一名警察少校絞刑，並判處一名涉案警察中校監禁七年。<br />\n<br />\n　　同日，伊拉克國會通過接納總理阿卜杜勒邁赫迪辭職。國會發表的聲明稱，國會將要求總統提名一位新總理。伊拉克群眾十月起因不滿政府腐敗、服務不力及高失業率，在全國多地爆發。反政府示威持續兩個月以來，已導致四百多人死亡及一萬五千人受傷。阿卜杜勒邁赫迪上周五宣布，將順應什葉派宗教領袖希斯塔尼的呼籲請辭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2106024/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%B3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E4%BC%8A%E6%8B%89%E5%85%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%A4%E7%B5%9E%E5%88%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2106024%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%2585%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%25B5%259E%25E5%2588%2591&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=0a3f433b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2106024%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%2585%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%25B5%259E%25E5%2588%2591&h=31579849\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2106024/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%B3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E4%BC%8A%E6%8B%89%E5%85%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%A4%E7%B5%9E%E5%88%91</a><br />\n<br />\n香港警察又領先全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\"